AccountTitlePrintOption.description: Options to indicate the multiple lists of account owner names. Possible Values: TitleNotPrinted, TitlePrintsBeforeNames, TitlePrintsAfterNames

CheckPrintOption.description: Options to indicate the multiple lists of account owner names. Possible Values: JointAnd, JointOr.

GenericPrintOption.description: Print options for the account or parties
